data.description: Competitivey priced OLD FARM Condo with 2 bedroom, 2 bath, 2 car garage. New Range, New Water heater, New Furnace, New Central Air, New deck carpet and Iron Rail. Located within 30 minutes of Utah's World Class Ski Resorts, The Old Farm Community is a park-like setting with over 1,000 mature trees and a serene stream meandering to a peaceful duck pond. The condo is accessible from the private parking garage. Each resident has their own 2-car private garage with ample storage, this unit also has a private storage closet not found in other garages.  Amenities include 2 swimming pools, one outdoor and one indoor pool, tennis courts/pickleball, Clubhouse and gym. This well-maintained condo is ready for your personal touch. Square footage is provided as a courtesy only and was obtained from original builder's marketing.
